nodes.text: The Ualaq were an Aqualish subspecies hailing from the planet Ando. Like the Quara subspecies, the Ualaq evolved from the baseline Aquala species[source?] and preferred living on land instead of in the water. While most Ualaq developed claw-like hands with five fingers, some Ualaq had three-fingered hands with very thick digits.[source?] Unlike the Quara and the Aquala, who had two eyes, the less-common Ualaq had four.
